nodes.text: Kelen Wordkal was a pilot who worked as a captain of the Mos Eisley police on the Outer Rim planet Tatooine. Wordkal often patrolled the Tatoo system in a Z-95 Headhunter.

Kelen Wordkal was a low-level, Tier 2 non-player character (NPC) in the Jump to Lightspeed portion of Star Wars Galaxies prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. His Z-95 could often be found in space near the Tatooine Space Station.
